  "features": [
    {
      "id": "F001",
      "phase": 1,
      "module": "client",
      "name": "修复 auth 弹窗重入 bug",
      "description": "修复 confirmDeviceKicked 和 confirmTokenExpired 中 clearAuthDialog() 在 disconnect/teardown 之前调用的问题。disconnect 触发 _onStatusChanged，lastCloseCode 仍为 4011/4001，_authDialogShowing 已清零，导致弹窗重复弹出。\n\n修复方案：将 clearAuthDialog() 移到 disconnectAll()/performSessionTeardown() 之后，确保守卫在 teardown 期间始终有效。",
      "verification": "F2",
      "depends_on": [],
      "status": "pending",
      "priority": 1,
      "acceptance_criteria": [
        "confirmDeviceKicked 中 clearAuthDialog() 在 disconnectAll() 之后调用",
        "confirmTokenExpired 中 clearAuthDialog() 在 performSessionTeardown() 之后调用",
        "disconnectAll()/performSessionTeardown() 期间 _onStatusChanged 触发时 _authDialogShowing 仍为 true，守卫生效",
        "被踢后弹窗不再重复弹出",
        "点击确定后能正常跳转登录页"
      ],
      "risk_tags": ["auth"],
      "fix_level": "L2",
      "root_cause_analysis": "clearAuthDialog() 先于 disconnectAll()/performSessionTeardown() 调用，导致 _authDialogShowing 守卫在 teardown 触发的状态变更回调中失效。4011/4001 close code 未被清除，_onStatusChanged 再次匹配条件并调用 _onDeviceKicked/_handleTokenExpired，弹窗重复弹出。多个 showDialog 的 modal barrier 叠加产生黑色闪烁，Navigator 被新弹窗打断导致登录按钮无效。",
      "similar_locations": [
        "confirmTokenExpired (terminal_screen_controller.dart:415-430) — 同样的 clearAuthDialog+teardown 模式",
        "_showTokenExpiredDialog (terminal_screen.dart:132-149) — token 过期弹窗，同属认证弹窗路径"
      ],
      "files": [
        "client/lib/screens/terminal_screen_controller.dart"
      ],
